products.title: Bengal Tiger Velour Twilight Curtain
products.description: Express your wild side with the bengal tiger twilight blue curtain, large green leaves on a contrasting teal blue background with a spectacular prowling tiger will add edge and a statement piece to any room in your home. Be bold and invest in this piece carefully selected from the prestigious journey beyond collection we know you won't regret this. At swift direct blinds, quality is important to us, which is why this curtain comes with their free five-year guarantee and customer-first service.
